        V5 --> V6[Admin Product Approval]
        V6 -->|Approved| V7[Products Listed]
        I --> V8[Vendor: Process Order]
        V8 --> V9{Confirm Shipping?}
        V9 -->|Yes| V10[Update Tracking Info]
        V9 -->|No| V11[Cancel Order]
